[I] Ultra fast grep with interactive TUI, fuzzy search, boolean queries

[T] Ultra fast grep with interactive TUI, fuzzy search, boolean queries,
[T] hexdumps and more: search file systems, source code, text, binary files,
[T] archives (cpio/tar/pax/zip), compressed files (gz/Z/bz2/lzma/xz/lz4/zstd),
[T] documents etc. A faster, user-friendly and compatible grep replacement.

